{"tid":1520690,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺牙朗好似保險佬咁羞家","createTime":"2019-08-31T02:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T03:03:15.000Z","uid":78336,"like":6,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9a78226cd39e800168db1cfee459de4dd0ad63f0","tid":1520690,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:43:44.000Z","msg":"一離開左皇馬完全比美欺比下去<br />\n今年除左歐聯頂死下體會之外 影都無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n18/19數據一覽<br />\n美斯以36g 13a排名西甲第一<br />\n牙朗得21g 8a 射手榜第四 助攻榜第八 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩個都係聯賽第一球會既主力 數據差天共地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">見到自己今年收晒皮 即刻冲出黎R美欺食飯</span><br />\n話自己同美斯係絕代雙驕 想提醒下大家 其實自己仲未退役 係同美斯同lv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時就話自己係史上最佳 無人同佢有得比<br />\n一柒左就掹美斯衫邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個情況仲要唔係第一次<br />\n上次牙朗斷崖式插水表現 都係話 同美斯並列史上最佳也不錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十足十d中學保險佬 以前係中學蝦蝦霸霸 目中無人<br />\n最後中六畢業<br />\n結果比佢串比佢恰既同學畢業做晒醫生工程師老師AO<br />\n即刻約人食飯拍晒膊頭話係中學好兄弟 中學既友誼係直到永遠 大學個d同學無得比 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b91a4abe3a9d741a2557f1e697bc19a77f7c9c","tid":1520690,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:44:24.000Z","msg":"有無朗迷出黎兜下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378520ace7ae4fbac581ba6fb57679b608d42371","tid":1520690,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c8277489cf232dcaccb3046aa15bdd24a16956","tid":1520690,"uid":268540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:52:54.000Z","msg":"美斯領先3球後反輸4球"},{"pid":"082f16bc9327fe6d8031c3f5cd74524d1b2bc3af","tid":1